title: BONUS Ep. #2 | Mini Update from Eric and Brian Nam
description:
Another bonus episode is here! Eric pops in to say hi and give you a mini update on what he's been up to while in Los Angeles. Yes, Eric and Brian are going crazy while stuck together in a house. How is your experience going? Stick until the end for an exciting announcement about a new show coming soon!
Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
